name: The World-Class Extras Walkthrough
author: COLDCAT
content: [God Dog]: I’m looking for someone to attempt life for a second time.At the joke-like chatting, I ended up responding with a joke.[JjamBbong Taste Clementine]: Second time, let’s go go go go.[God Dog]: Are you confident? It’s not going to be easy, you know?[JjamBbong Taste Clementine]: Don’t I just have to do the same thing over again in this shitty game? Hehehehe.But the result of this…“The third prince of the Magic Kingdom, Guillaume!”“……Who?”I became the third prince inside of that game.An ee
